						<p>Pāṇḍya, Sundarapāṇḍya, 16th year = 13th Century.</p>						

						<p>The Śivabrāhmaṇas of Tiruvaiyāṟuḍaiya-nāyaṉār temple at Chembāḍu received some temple. land for offerings in a <hi rend="italic">sandhi.</hi> This may be related to the above record.</p>						

