<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> tiripuvaṉaccakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> cuntarapāṇṭiya tEvaṟku yāṇṭu patiṉāṟā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>vatu <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yaciṅka kulakāla vaḷanāṭṭu kuḷamaṅkala ṉāṭṭuc cempāṭāṉa cempiyaṉ
<lb n="3"/>puttāmpūr Uṭaiyār tiruvaiyāṟuṭaiya ṉāyiṉār kōyil muppatu vaṭṭa
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ttu kāṇi Uṭaiya civappirāmaṇarrōm Ikkōyil Āvuṭaiyār Āṇṭa
<lb n="5"/>kūttaṟkum tampirāṭṭiyāṟkum Upaiyamāka Aṟuṉāḻi Aricikkum kaṟi Amutum
<lb n="6"/>Uppamutum miḷakamutu Uṭpaṭa maṟavākalum maṟavaṉ vayakkal kiṇaṟṟil pā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>tiyuṅ kār vayakkalum kaikkoṇṭu Ippaṭi cantirātittavarai Upaiyamāka
<lb n="8"/>Oru canti cellakkaṭavatāka kaikkoṇṭōm §
</p>

